{
  "stem": "23498.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was '42. '42, and you see, that place where my father worked, it was [INAUDIBLE], that shop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother was going somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know whether to get some milk, or-- I can't recall at this moment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was called, but my father told us one thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we were-- and mostly to my mother, he told, because he knew that we wouldn't go far.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my mother, if she goes out of the shop, she has to be careful to be in the last line, close to the gates, to the houses.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from that angle, it would be easier to run away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that what she did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was somewhere in [INAUDIBLE], or some other street where she was caught.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all the-- all the people were walking, and she tried to be last, and last, and last.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the German turned around, and she went to the gate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it-- it-- what-- what come out is that it was sort of her-- not a fishing village, but, underground, you know, where the cellars are, it was an enormous labyrinth-- you know-- all white-- and it comes out that they were keeping fish, you know, because they weren't any fridges.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- it was cool.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was an enormous place, because from that place, before the war, they were sort of sending the fish to all the markets or shops, something like that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother went there, and lie on the ground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she stayed there maybe half a day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was afraid to come out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When she wanted to come out, it was already the night, but she couldn't come-- she couldn't find the way.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was so, you know, rounded in all directions, she couldn't find the way.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
